description: THC Therapeutics, Inc. operates in the wellness industry. It is involved in the development of dHydronator, a sanitizing herb dryer for drying and sanitizing of freshly harvested cannabis, other herbs, flowers, and tea leaves. The company was formerly known as Millennium Blockchain, Inc. and changed its name to THC Therapeutics, Inc. in September 2018. THC Therapeutics, Inc. was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Las Vegas, Nevada.
